import React from 'react' import TextPage from '../components/TextPage' const PrivacyPolicy = () => { return (

privacy policy for Gustav apps

Effective Date: 19. 2. 2024

Developer: Dalibor Janeček

Introduction

The Gustav Timer and Gustav Weights apps, developed by Dalibor Janeček, are committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information within our apps. Given that the Gustav Timer and Gustav Weights apps do not collect or process any user personal data, the scope of these policies is minimal.

Personal Data

The Gustav Timer and Gustav Weights apps do not collect, store, or process any personal data from their users. This means that the apps do not require registration, login, or any personal information from users.

Tracking and Cookies

We do not use any tracking technologies such as cookies, beacons, tags, or similar tracking technologies.

Security

We are committed to protecting the security of your information. Since we do not acquire or store any personal data, no special measures are required to protect your data.

Changes to Privacy Policy

The developer reserves the right to update or change these privacy policies at any time. Any changes will become effective immediately after the updated policies are posted on the app pages or otherwise communicated to users.

Contact

If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy policy, please contact the developer, Dalibor Janeček.

 ) } export default PrivacyPolicy
